Package org.apache.ignite.mxbean

Contains annotations for Dynamic MBeans.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BaselineAutoAdjustMXBean
    This interface defines JMX view on DistributedBaselineConfiguration.
    ClientProcessorMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    ClusterMetricsMXBean
    Cluster metrics MBean.
    ComputeMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    DataStorageMXBean
    An MX bean allowing to monitor and tune persistence.
    DefragmentationMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    EncryptionMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    FailureHandlingMxBean
    MBean that controls critical failure handling.
    IgniteClusterMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    IgniteMBeanAware
    MBean-aware interface.
    IgniteMXBean
    This interface defines JMX view on kernal.
    IgnitionMXBean
    This interface defines JMX view on Ignition.
    MetricsMxBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    PerformanceStatisticsMBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    QueryMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    ServiceMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    SnapshotMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    TransactionMetricsMxBean Deprecated.
    Check the JmxMetricExporterSpi with "name=\"tx\"" instead.
    TransactionsMXBean
    Transactions MXBean interface.
    WarmUpMXBean Deprecated.
    Use managements API beans, instead.
    WorkersControlMXBean
    MBean that provides ability to terminate worker that registered in the workers registry.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    MXBeanDescription
    Provides description for MBean classes and methods.
    MXBeanParameter
    Provides name and description for MBean method parameter.
    MXBeanParametersDescriptions Deprecated.
    Use MXBeanParameter instead.
    MXBeanParametersNames Deprecated.
    Use MXBeanParameter instead.
